      "description": "This E92-generation M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, powered by the S65 naturally aspirated V8 paired with a three-pedal 6-speed manual transmission. The engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system to deliver linear power up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The mechanical limited-slip differential and M-specific kinematic suspension geometry provide exceptional turn-in and mid-corner stability. Recent service includes rod bearing prophylaxis and fresh bushings across the rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity. The exterior and interior reflect careful ownership with minor cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, making it a mechanically robust example of the last high-revving, non-aspirated M-cars.",
